result.reason: Feature request has no body/specification — multi-user security scope (RBAC, per-user ACLs, AD integration, audit logging) is undefined and cannot be triaged without requirements.
result.approach: Request detailed specification: what 'multi-user security' means (role-based access, per-connection permissions, audit trail, LDAP/AD auth), how many users are expected, and whether SQL-mode or XML-mode connections file is the target.
